        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2709",
        "content": "The campaign became a very hot one during which most of the militancy seemed to be on the side of the political leaders. Heavy fists came down on desks.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
