        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2709",
        "content": "They had answered the call and they meant to stay in the fight until it was won.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2709_158074_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2709/158074/2709_158074_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2709",
        "content": "The envoys, symbolic of the new strength that was to come out of the West, made their journey across continent by automobile.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2709_158074_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2709/158074/2709_158074_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2709",
        "content": "They created a sensation all along the way, received as they were by governors, by mayors, by officials high and low, and by the populace.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2709_158074_000026_000000",
