        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2709",
        "content": "And so the hearing passed in something of a verbal riot, but with no doubt as to the fact that Congressmen were alarmed by the prospect of women voting as a protest group.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
