        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2709",
        "content": "The Republican National Convention, meeting immediately. after the Woman's Party Convention, and the Democratic National Convention the week following, both included suffrage planks in their national platforms for the first time in history.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
